00:05:04.090 --> 00:05:06.410
But if there are two
or three things I'd say

00:05:06.410 --> 00:05:08.640
that World War I definitely
accomplishes is, one,

00:05:08.640 --> 00:05:11.710
is that a number of key
figures later in World War I --

00:05:11.710 --> 00:05:14.670
serve in World War
I and prove critical

00:05:14.670 --> 00:05:16.020
to 20th century developments later.

00:05:16.020 --> 00:05:20.170 position:56%
So FDR, the secretary of the navy
who draws upon his experiences there

00:05:20.170 --> 00:05:24.600
to create the new deal and then
obviously prosecute World War II.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:28.690
Charles Hamilton Houston, who goes
to war, comes back really kind of,

00:05:28.690 --> 00:05:29.990
embittered is not the right word,

00:05:29.990 --> 00:05:31.930
but like critical social
consciousness about racism,

00:05:31.930 --> 00:05:35.390 position:56%
