out in the marketplace.

00:07:13.520 --> 00:07:15.510
You know, a very --
a very sharp shift.

00:07:15.510 --> 00:07:18.150
And our idea of civil liberties
today, and this is something

00:07:18.150 --> 00:07:22.110
that Geoffrey Stone and David
Rabban talk about in their work,

00:07:22.110 --> 00:07:23.600
